	- INCOMPATIBLE CHANGE: remove dependency on, and autoloading
          of AnyEvent::Fork.
        - do not call Array::Heap::adjust_heap_idx with out of bound
          array index on destroy, use a gentler way to shut down
          (reported by Robert Schmidt).

